  <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-heading">服务质量</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="icon row-bottom-padded-sm"><span class="fa fa-diamond fa-5x" aria-hidden="true"></span></div>
          <h2>地理优越</h2>
          <p>位于市中心附近，交通便利，随时可以出入各大赌场，最快倾家荡产的正确选择。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="icon row-bottom-padded-sm"><span class="fa fa-bolt fa-5x" aria-hidden="true"></span></div>
          <h2>方便快捷</h2>
          <p>只要肯花钱，没有办不到的事。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="icon row-bottom-padded-sm"><span class="fa fa-heart fa-5x" aria-hidden="true"></span></div>
          <h2>大家的选择</h2>
          <p>每年有超过三千的富翁入住我们的酒店变成负翁，提供天桥指路服务，输光之后随时能拎包入住。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="product-screenshots">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12 section-heading text-center">
      <h2>客房服务</h2>
      <div class="row text-center">
          <h3>北海全鱼台北茶,京华特色菜肴佳. 金堂客点扒猪脸,三寿宾欣斑节虾. 元帅多怀脑羹味,酒人尽爱牛鞭花. 家常白玉汤园美,好鼓掌声贯彩霞.</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="owl-carousel-center">
    <div><%=image_tag 'rooms/screen-1-1-login.jpg' %></div>
    <div><%=image_tag 'rooms/screen-2-1-login.jpg' %></div>
    <div><%=image_tag 'rooms/screen-1-8-list.jpg' %></div>
    <div><%=image_tag 'rooms/screen-2-6-overview.jpg' %></div>
    <div><%=image_tag 'rooms/screen-3-7-groups.jpg' %></div>
    <div><%=image_tag 'rooms/screen-4-7-groups.jpg' %></div>
    <div><%=image_tag 'rooms/screen-5-6-overview.jpg' %></div>
</div>

<script>
  $('.owl-carousel-center').owlCarousel({
    center: true,
    items:2,
    loop:false,
    margin:10,
    nav: true,
    dots: true,
    autoHeight: true,
    smartSpeed: 500,
    autoplay: true,
    autoplayTimeout: 5000,
    autoplayHoverPause: true,
    responsive:{
      0:{
        items:1
      },
      600:{
        items:4
      },
      1000:{
        items:5
      }
    }
  });
  $('body').on('click', '.owl-item', function(){
    var $this = $(this),
    index = $this.index();
    $('.owl-carousel-center .owl-dots > div').eq(index).trigger('click');
  });
</script>